OL,3,CRough sleepers appeal for pods to
OL,4,Cremain open over Christmas
OL,6,FA homeless man in Exeter has told ITV
OL,7,FNews he has been left with no option
OL,8,Fbut to cope on the streets this
OL,9,FChristmas following the temporary
OL,10,Fclosure of accommodation pods he's
OL,11,Fbeen using.
OL,13,FFour pods in Howell Road Car Park,
OL,14,Fwhich offer a safe place for homeless
OL,15,Fpeople to sleep, are due to close on
OL,16,FThursday 19 December until the new
OL,17,Fyear.
