OL,3,CRough sleepers appeal for pods to
OL,4,Cremain open over Christmas
OL,6,FExeter City Council said "reduced
OL,7,Fstaffing" has given it no option but
OL,8,Fto close the pods over the festive
OL,9,Fseason.
OL,11,FBut Kebba Sarge, who has lived in and
OL,12,Faround Exeter for 9 years, is
OL,13,Fappealing to the council to keep the
OL,14,Fpods open saying it provides a vital
OL,15,Froof over his head.
OL,17,F"This is all I've got," Mr Sarge told
OL,18,FITV West Country.
