OL,3,CRough sleepers appeal for pods to
OL,4,Cremain open over Christmas
OL,6,F"If they leave it open, they will save
OL,7,Four life, but if they close the pods,
OL,8,Fwe won't eat or wash for days".
OL,10,FThe pods were introduced in 2023, to
OL,11,Fprovide a safe place for rough
OL,12,Fsleepers who had "no alternative
OL,13,Faccommodation," the council said.
OL,15,FEach pod has a bed, a toilet and a USB
OL,16,Fcharging port, as well as keyless
OL,17,Fentry and solar powered lighting.
OL,19,FMr Sarge said the pods offer him a
OL,20,F"lifeline".
