OL,3,CRough sleepers appeal for pods to
OL,4,Cremain open over Christmas
OL,6,F"If they keep them open, we can help
OL,7,Fourselves. We don't have any water, or
OL,8,Felectric. We don't get any food. It's
OL,9,Fonly the cleaning of the toilet that
OL,10,Fwe won't get".
OL,12,F"We want them to give us a chance, but
OL,13,FI can't make that decision. They're
OL,14,Fprofessional, they know what they're
OL,15,Fdoing but if they can give us life,
OL,16,Fit's a life for me".
