OL,3,CRough sleepers appeal for pods to
OL,4,Cremain open over Christmas
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,7,FExeter City Council said: "The
OL,8,Ftemporary closure is due to reduced
OL,9,Fstaffing over the period, not just at
OL,10,Fthe Council but partners and the
OL,11,Fancillary services needed for the pods
OL,12,Fto run.
OL,14,F"All clients currently living in the
OL,15,Fpods have been made aware of the
OL,16,Fclosure, and services are working with
OL,17,Fthem to find alternative housing
OL,18,Fpathways.
